<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist Dr. Edwin J. Feulner, Jr.</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>

<img src="/townhall/columnists/colm.gif">






</center>





<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-feulner.html.cgi/textonly">[Text View]</a></h5>

<center>
<h2>Dr. Edwin J. Feulner, Jr.</h2>
</center>


<p>


<img align="left" alt="Photo of Dr. Edwin J. Feulner, Jr." 
hspace=8 vspace=25 src="/heritage/staff/pics/feulner.gif">


<a href="/townhall/columnists/feulner.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
<UL>
<li>January 23, 1997 <a href="/heritage/commentary/97/op-ef34.html">Defending Gingrich</a>
<li>January 23, 1997 <a href="/heritage/commentary/97/op-ef33.html">It's In The Water</a>
<li>December 19, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef32.html">Crime Can Be Whipped</a>
<li>November 25, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef31.html">A Celebration of Indoctrination</a>
<li>November 25, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef30.html">Why It's So Hard To Save</a> 
<li>August 22, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef29.html">Wasting Your Money</a>
<li>August 22, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef28.html">Truth in Testimony</a>
<li>July 25, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef27.html">Socially Responsible Business</a> 
<li>July 25, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef26.html">Dumb and Dumber</a> 


<li>June 27, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef25.html">Politicking on the Workers' Dime</a>
<li>June 27, 1996 <a href="/heritage/commentary/op-ef24.html">Tune in to Talk Radio</a>

